OL,3,CHow can I lower my energy bills and
OL,4,Cwhat help is there for me?
OL,6,FHouseholds across Britain are facing
OL,7,Fincreasing energy costs this winter
OL,8,Fafter the regulator raised its price
OL,9,Fcap from October.
OL,11,FOfgem's price cap is rising by #149
OL,12,Ffrom the current #1,568 a year for a
OL,13,Ftypical household in England, Scotland
OL,14,Fand Wales to #1,717.
OL,16,FITV News looks at why the price cap is
OL,17,Fgoing up and what people can do to
OL,18,Fmitigate the cost of their energy
OL,19,Fbills.
