OL,3,CHow can I lower my energy bills and
OL,4,Cwhat help is there for me?
OL,6,FThe energy price cap sets a maximum
OL,7,Fprice that energy suppliers can charge
OL,8,Fconsumers in England, Scotland and
OL,9,FWales for each kilowatt hour (kWh) of
OL,10,Fenergy they use.
OL,12,FThe figures provided by Ofgem indicate
OL,13,Fwhat a household using gas and
OL,14,Felectricity, and paying by direct
OL,15,Fdebit, can expect to pay if their
OL,16,Fenergy consumption is typical.
