OL,3,CHow can I lower my energy bills and
OL,4,Cwhat help is there for me?
OL,6,FIt is important to note that it does
OL,7,Fnot limit a home's total bills because
OL,8,Fpeople still pay for the amount of
OL,9,Fenergy they use ` so if it is above
OL,10,Fthe average they will pay more, and if
OL,11,Fit is below they will pay less.
OL,13,FEnergy is regulated separately in
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland.
