OL,3,CHow can I lower my energy bills and
OL,4,Cwhat help is there for me?
OL,6,FOfgem said the main reason why it has
OL,7,Fdecided to increase the cap is because
OL,8,Fof rising wholesale prices in the
OL,9,Finternational energy market, which
OL,10,Fhave been caused by heightened
OL,11,Fgeopolitical tensions and extreme
OL,12,Fweather events.
OL,14,FWhat can I do to lower my bills?
OL,16,FMartin Lewis, the founder of
OL,17,FMoneySavingExpert.com, said people
OL,18,F"can and should save by switching"
OL,19,Ftheir energy supplier, and consider a
OL,20,Ffixed-price energy tariff."
