OL,3,CHow can I lower my energy bills and
OL,4,Cwhat help is there for me?
OL,6,FThe cheapest year-long fixes on the
OL,7,Fmarket right now are about 7% less
OL,8,Fthan the new October price cap, but
OL,9,Fthey might not be around long," he
OL,10,Fcautioned.
OL,12,FMr Lewis suggested that people look
OL,13,Ffor the cheapest option for their use
OL,14,Fand location, and they can use
OL,15,Fcomparison sites to find and compare
OL,16,Fdeals.
