OL,3,CHow can I lower my energy bills and
OL,4,Cwhat help is there for me?
OL,6,FEmily Seymour, energy editor at
OL,7,FWhich?, said: "Unfortunately, there's
OL,8,Fno 'one size fits all' approach when
OL,9,Fit comes to fixing an energy deal as
OL,10,Fit will all depend on your individual
OL,11,Fcircumstances.
OL,13,F"You should compare what your monthly
OL,14,Fpayments would be on a fixed deal with
OL,15,Fwhat you'd expect them to be if you
OL,16,Fremain with the price-capped variable
OL,17,Ftariff to see what the best option is
OL,18,Ffor you.
