OL,3,CHow can I lower my energy bills and
OL,4,Cwhat help is there for me?
OL,6,F"As a rule of thumb, we'd recommend
OL,7,Flooking for deals around the price of
OL,8,Fthe current price cap, not longer than
OL,9,F12 months and without significant exit
OL,10,Ffees."
OL,12,FWhat support is available for me?
OL,14,FOfgem urged people to make the most of
OL,15,Fany state benefits they are entitled
OL,16,Fto, which could help with paying
OL,17,Fenergy bills as well as the wider cost
OL,18,Fof living.
