OL,3,CHow can I lower my energy bills and
OL,4,Cwhat help is there for me?
OL,6,FAround 1.4 million pensioners are
OL,7,Falready receiving pension credit, but
OL,8,Fthe Government estimates up to 880,000
OL,9,Ffurther households are eligible for
OL,10,Fthe support for those with a low
OL,11,Fincome.
OL,13,FPeople receiving pension credit
OL,14,Fqualify for the winter fuel payment
OL,15,Fworth up to #300, to help with bills.
OL,17,FPreviously, anyone over state pension
OL,18,Fage could receive the payment, but
OL,19,Fthis was changed by the new
OL,20,FGovernment, meaning about 10 million
OL,21,Fpensioners will miss out this year.
