OL,3,CHow can I lower my energy bills and
OL,4,Cwhat help is there for me?
OL,6,FPeople are encouraged to contact their
OL,7,Fenergy supplier if they are worried
OL,8,Fabout paying their bills.
OL,10,FEnergy companies are required to work
OL,11,Fwith customers to agree on a payment
OL,12,Fplan they can afford, which could mean
OL,13,Fmore flexibility over how and at what
OL,14,Ftime people pay.
